beer.beer_description: This particular beer is slightly hazy, brewed with heaps of pilsner malt, fermented with our house lager yeast and contains very little residual sugar. Its near bone-dry and crispy as. We brewed it with an out-of-sight combination of Falconers Flight, Huell Melon, Mosaic and Citra hops. New world hop characters abound; tropical aromas interplay with ripe fruit flavours and a supportive bitterness keeps the elbow bent.
